{
  "stem": "17135.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 343.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because revolt is-- is punished by death.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They apparently were compelled to send so and so many people to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And-- and-- and-- and he didn't probably want to admit to Berlin, to the Gestapo, that they were so ineffective that people could revolt.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It's unheard of.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It would have put a black-- it would have put his name in-- in-- in-- in-- in-- in jeopardy.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And SS officers that did not behave, and didn't do a good job, were sent to the front-- to the Eastern Front-- which meant certain death.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And they didn't want to do that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that is my explanation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the reason why they didn't kill us all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they have to give a report, there was revolt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would like to ask you one more thing about the revolt.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Do you remember how it started?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Were you any part of it?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I told you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were-- I even remember some of their names.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH], they went around-- only the younger people-- among the younger people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were actually at that time, at the disinfection--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--hangar.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would say, young people, at least about a hundred.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From the age of 15 to 25.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe even 120.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he convinced us-- we were so demoralized to be there two days-- and the rumors, I mean, rumors were-- were growing day by-- hour by hour.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they said, we have the feeling that the actually intention of the SS [INAUDIBLE] is to kill us all.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So if we get killed, why not get killed like heroes-- as in-- like human beings.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You want to hear something?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I really was scared to death.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I believed they really would kill us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They would gas us.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
